The paper deals with transforming point clouds by replacing objects with their semantically equivalent counterparts, which has applications in virtual reality, repair of fused scans, and robotics. This involves semantic labeling and object replacement, which are both topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also presents numerical tools for efficient optimization, which falls under the category of optimization and control (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques for semantic labeling and object replacement, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
